    dc:description "Figure 2. (a–c) Eurysthea tatianakozlovae sp. nov., holotype female: (a) dorsal habitus; (b) ventral habitus; (c) lateral habitus. (d–f) Eurysthea nearnsi sp. nov., holotype male: (d) dorsal habitus; (e) ventral habitus; (f) lateral habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5183946/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5183948>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Detail of elytra. (a) Eurysthea antonkozlovi sp. nov.; (b) Eurysthea barsevskisi sp. nov.; (c) Eurysthea tatianakozlovae sp. nov.; (d) Eurysthea nearnsi sp. nov. Arrows show the lanceolate setae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5183948/files/figure.png" ;
